metadata.name: Kombat Kiwis #1
metadata.description: Kiwis are marching for war! Since Australia fell to the Emus, the Kiwis knew it would only be a matter of time before they set their murderous sights on their own island home. Prepare these troops for battle, as they will need to fight on the beaches, on the landing grounds, the fields, the streets and the hills. Never give up, never surrender. For King and for Country! For the Moa God!
